Richardson maturity level to evaluates rest services:

level 0 : exposing soap web services in rest style
     http://server/getPosts
     http://server/deletePosts
     
level 1: Expose resource with proper URI (Improper HTTP methods)
    http://server/accounts
    http://server/accounts/10
    
level 2 : level 1 with use of proper HTTP methods

level 3 : level 2 with HATEOAS

### Best practices for Rest services design:
1. Think of consumer first
2. Create great document for APIs (using swagger)
3. Use proper HTTP methods
4. USe proper URI
    